t_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9764,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/10\/allah-loves-hilm-haya\/","url_meta":{"origin":3591,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Akhlaq: Allah loves forbearance, clemency","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 10, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said to Al-Ashajj 'Abdul Qays, \u201cVerily, you have two qualities beloved to Allah: forbearance and clemency.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 17 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d\u00a0\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u0634\u064e\u062c\u0650\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":597,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/03\/03\/rahmah-99-yawm-al-qiyamah\/","url_meta":{"origin":3591,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Rahmah: Ninety-nine parts of mercy for Judgment Day","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 3, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Salman al-Farisi reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, on the day Allah created the heavens and the earth, He created one hundred parts of mercy. Each part can fill what is between the heavens and the earth. He made one part of mercy\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2037,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/03\/believers-like-body\/","url_meta":{"origin":3591,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Brotherhood: Believers are one body in compassion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Nu\u2019man ibn Bashir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe parable\u00a0of the believers in their affection, mercy, and compassion for each other is that of a body. When any limb aches, the whole body reacts with sleeplessness and fever.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6011, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Featured&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Featured","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/featured\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":30912,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/24\/hasan-aql-kindness-half\/","url_meta":{"origin":3591,"position":4},"title":"Hasan on &#8216;Aql: Loving kindness is half of sound reason","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 24, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abi Dunya reported: Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \"Loving kindness towards people is half of reason.\" Source:\u00a0Muda\u0304ra\u0304t al-Na\u0304s 44 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0646\u064a\u0627 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u00a0\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0